A dual‑track NIL valuation, reporting, and exchange system integrating BiomechFlow™ physiological intelligence, NIL Intel (NIL Swaps), and the BLEI‑E Multi‑Asset Risk Engine.

This repository is the NIL economics layer of the broader Biometric Finance Stack, connecting athlete physiology → NIL valuation → equity‑market risk.

Overview

This project implements the world’s first institutional‑grade NIL valuation and exchange system, designed for:

    College athletics (Track A)

    Professional NIL markets & derivative exposure (Track B)

    Sponsor, agency, and franchise valuation workflows

    Integration with BLEI‑E factor modeling

    BiomechFlow™ biometric intelligence ingestion

The system is built on real code — TypeScript, Node, PostgreSQL, React — and is designed for bank‑grade deployment, hedge‑fund‑grade analytics, and sports‑ops usability.

